108
00:07:56,209 --> 00:08:00,112
Oh, anatomy class is
such a headache for me.

109
00:08:00,112 --> 00:08:02,512
You always do well anyways.

110
00:08:03,583 --> 00:08:05,448
What a great day!

111
00:08:05,985 --> 00:08:07,009
Why?

112
00:08:18,030 --> 00:08:20,089
- Hui-jae
- Huh?

113
00:08:22,001 --> 00:08:23,161
Wait a sec.

114
00:08:24,070 --> 00:08:25,162
Hey.

115
00:08:38,651 --> 00:08:40,551
