137
00:11:19,845 --> 00:11:21,142
- Hui-jae
- Pass!

138
00:11:22,481 --> 00:11:25,939
She's not on our team!
You idiot!

139
00:11:40,733 --> 00:11:42,496
- One to six!
- Six to four!

140
00:11:42,601 --> 00:11:44,193
- Four to three!
- Three to two!

141
