162
00:13:03,349 --> 00:13:04,839
I'm sorry.

163
00:13:09,388 --> 00:13:10,946
Let's go.

164
00:13:27,740 --> 00:13:29,002
Hui-jae!

165
00:13:30,509 --> 00:13:33,239
You look so comfortable there!

166
