the Han River

170
00:13:53,399 --> 00:13:55,424
next to the highway.

171
00:14:41,313 --> 00:14:43,716
Is it inconvenient for you,
having so many of us here?

172
00:14:43,716 --> 00:14:46,378
Not at all! Having you here
brings the place to life.

173
00:14:46,919 --> 00:14:48,079
Sorry for the trouble!

174
00:14:48,153 --> 00:14:50,087
Oh, it's no problem.

175
00:15:28,260 --> 00:15:30,160
So, should we read
"The Fox and the Crane?"

176
00:15:30,229 --> 00:15:31,719
Yes!

177
00:15:32,097 --> 00:15:33,860
