Be sure to stir it well,
so it doesn't stick together.

215
00:18:00,846 --> 00:18:01,813
Okay.

216
00:18:04,750 --> 00:18:05,944
Save some for us.

217
00:18:06,118 --> 00:18:08,109
That rice wine is great!

218
