presiding over the club...

247
00:19:30,702 --> 00:19:33,364
Words like enthusiasm,
sincerity and responsibility

248
00:19:33,438 --> 00:19:35,269
all fit her perfectly.

249
00:19:36,375 --> 00:19:39,344
You sound like a man
bragging about his wife.

250
00:19:43,815 --> 00:19:46,079
KANG Dong-hyun! Come up.

251
00:19:47,953 --> 00:19:49,352
Good for you!

252
00:19:49,488 --> 00:19:50,978
Nice job.

253
00:19:54,293 --> 00:19:56,090
- KIM Tae-hyun!
- Yes!

254
00:19:56,161 --> 00:19:57,856
Come on up.

255
00:19:59,731 --> 00:20:01,926
- Nice work, Tae-hyun.
- Thank you.

256
00:20:05,971 --> 00:20:09,338
