257
00:20:11,810 --> 00:20:14,210
Sure, what is it?

258
00:20:14,646 --> 00:20:16,671
Swim up to there and back.

259
00:20:19,518 --> 00:20:22,282
You see the red flag? To there.

260
00:20:22,588 --> 00:20:23,486
